{"results":[{"aya":"008","id":5856,"locale":"fr","sura":"083","text":"et qui te dira ce qu'est le Sijjîn? -","translator":"Muhammad Hamidullah"},{"aya":"009","id":5857,"locale":"fr","sura":"083","text":"Un livre déjà cacheté (achevé).","translator":"Muhammad Hamidullah"},{"aya":"010","id":5858,"locale":"fr","sura":"083","text":"Malheur, ce jour-là, aux négateurs,","translator":"Muhammad Hamidullah"},{"aya":"011","id":5859,"locale":"fr","sura":"083","text":"qui démentent le jour de la Rétribution.","translator":"Muhammad Hamidullah"},{"aya":"012","id":5860,"locale":"fr","sura":"083","text":"Or, ne le dément que tout transgresseur, pécheur:","translator":"Muhammad Hamidullah"},{"aya":"013","id":5861,"locale":"fr","sura":"083","text":"qui, lorsque Nos versets lui sont récités, dit: «[Ce sont] des contes d'anciens!»","translator":"Muhammad Hamidullah"},{"aya":"014","id":5862,"locale":"fr","sura":"083","text":"Pas du tout, mais ce qu'ils ont accompli couvre leurs cœurs.","translator":"Muhammad Hamidullah"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":6,"previousPage":"/fr/s083.json","nextPage":"/fr/s083-3.json"}}